For the stir-fried vegetables, in a hot wok add the sesame oil, chilli and aubergine.  Cook for three minutes and add the reminder of the ingredients and cook for a further minute.For the omelette, in a bowl mix all the ingredients for the omelette together.In a medium-sized non-stick frying pan place the mixture into the pan and cook for two minutes over a medium heat.Add into it the stir-fried vegetables and fold the omelette over, cook for a further minute and serve.